# Cursor Rules for Grants Snap Project

## Project Overview
This is a Grants Snap project with Supabase integration.

## Development Guidelines
- Use TypeScript for all new code
- Follow the existing component structure
- Use the established Supabase hooks for data operations
- Follow the existing Supabase integration patterns

## File Structure
- `src/lib/supabase.ts` - Supabase client configuration
- `src/hooks/useAuth.ts` - Authentication hooks
- `src/hooks/useOpportunities.ts` - Opportunities data hooks
- `src/hooks/useProfile.ts` - Profile management hooks 